Algorithm: Calculate Regression Coefficients
Start
Initialize two lists x and y
Find number of elements n
Calculate mean of x → mx
Calculate mean of y → my
Calculate slope b1:
Find sum of (x[i] - mx) * (y[i] - my)
Find sum of (x[i] - mx)²
Divide both values → b1
Calculate intercept b0:
b0 = my - (b1 * mx)
Print b0 and b1
Stop
